=\"wp-image-2173\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-01.jpg 870w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-01-370x179.jpg 370w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-01-600x290.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-01-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-01-768x371.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">  The Best in Beauty <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p> Los Angeles\u2013based blogger&nbsp;was one of the first ladies to bring laid-back yet elevated California style to the front row of fashion week. We love her sensibility for giving the Cali-girl vibe a unique twist. <br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped wp-block-gallery-2 is-layout-flex wp-block-gallery-is-layout-flex\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"870\" height=\"420\" src=\"http:\/\/slk54.ru\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"2178\" data-link=\"http:\/\/slk54.ru\/easiest-houseplants-to-grow-in-the-bedroom\/single-blog-06\/\" class=\"wp-image-2178\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06.jpg 870w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06-370x179.jpg 370w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06-600x290.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-06-768x371.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"870\" height=\"420\" src=\"http:\/\/slk54.ru\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"2177\" data-link=\"http:\/\/slk54.ru\/easiest-houseplants-to-grow-in-the-bedroom\/single-blog-05\/\" class=\"wp-image-2177\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05.jpg 870w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05-370x179.jpg 370w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05-600x290.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-05-768x371.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 870px) 100vw, 870px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">  Fashion on World <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p> The first thing you need when you\u2019re shopping on eBay is patience. It takes a little time and dedication to find exactly what you\u2019re looking for, and that\u2019s what I experienced when on the hunt for these iconic, quilted combat boots. Here are my top tips for shopping on eBay: <br><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\"><li>Parts of the Whole<\/li><li>Anticipating the Wants of the Consumer<\/li><li>Constant Adaptation<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed-youtube wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"Dior | Fall Winter 2019\/2020 Full Fashion Show | Exclusive\" width=\"768\" height=\"432\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/JJHLgD6uqf0?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\">  Parts of the Whole <\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\" class=\"has-drop-cap\">The fashion world\u2019s finest plus one impeccably turned out Celine Dion, couture week\u2019s unofficial newly crowned queen braved a European heatwave to attend Fall 2019 Couture Week, and the beauty looks alone were worth sweating it out for.  There was the bold: gravity-defying fanned out \u201980s hair at Givenchy, glitter-encrusted upper eyelids at Valentino .<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"alignright is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"http:\/\/slk54.ru\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-2176\" width=\"318\" height=\"154\" srcset=\"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04.jpg 870w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04-370x179.jpg 370w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04-600x290.jpg 600w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04-300x145.jpg 300w, https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/07\/single-blog-04-768x371.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 318px) 100vw, 318px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">In simplest terms, the fashion industry could be described as the business of making clothes, but that would omit the important distinction between fashion and apparel.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p style=\"text-align:left\">Apparel is functional clothing, one of humanity&#8217;s basic needs, but fashion incorporates its own prejudices of style, individual taste, and&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.encyclopedia.com\/earth-and-environment\/ecology-and-environmentalism\/environmental-studies\/cultural-evolution\">cultural evolution<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>In the 1930s, though, as the unified center for garment production, even limited to the business of making clothes, its components have continually adapted to the changes of fashion and prevailing consumer demands, whether for casual clothes or formal suits, American sportswear or street wear.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Fashion is the color of life The blog features some amazing fashion inspiration pictures of Amy. She exudes a sophisticated but comfortable vibe. Amy typically rocks chic street fashion ensembles matched with jumpsuits, slim pants or skinny jeans, and layered neatly with leather jackets or blazers, and streamlined with some sneakers. Searching for online style [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":2214,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[30],"tags":[37,39,45],"class_list":["post-15","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-accessories","tag-bikini","tag-hand-bag","tag-vest"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=15"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/15\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/2214"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=15"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=15"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xn--54-1lcd3a.xn--p1ai\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=15"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}